The hole and electron mobility of the D/A blend film was measured using the space charge limited current (SCLC) method. The structure of hole-only device and electron-only mobility device is ITO/PEDOT: PSS/Active layer/Au and ITO/ZnO/ Active layer/Ag, respectively. The mobility was determined by fitting the dark current to the model of a single carrier SCLC, which is described by the equation:J=98εoεrμhV2d3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
